  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Forge is a puzzle game where you create pixel art by connecting nodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rabbit turns into a bird, and a bird becomes a dolphin?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A seahorse and a dragon merge into a rapper?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With just nodes, anything is possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each of the over 50 nodes, including Add, Subtract, Shift, Rotate, Split, and Combine, has its own unique function.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect these nodes in various ways to transform pixel art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Grayscale World, to RGB World, to Alpha World, to Emission World, and to Motion World where pixel art is animated, explore five worlds with different characteristics, and discover mind-blowing puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 stages across 5 worlds, each with its own unique personality.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic stages always introduce new nodes every time, allowing you to organically learn how they work.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced stages make use of the nodes learned in the basic stages in various ways.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There can be multiple ways to solve a puzzle. Use over 50 nodes to find your own solution.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contains a built-in hint system. Use hints if you get stuck!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Has an original soundtrack.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/dee08d9f892b3fc3113e196e4d9996e4.poster.avif?t=1773995248\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/dee08d9f892b3fc3113e196e4d9996e4.webm?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/dee08d9f892b3fc3113e196e4d9996e4.mp4?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/136f13af9b82e7d48909d2f9bb689664.poster.avif?t=1773995248\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/136f13af9b82e7d48909d2f9bb689664.webm?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/136f13af9b82e7d48909d2f9bb689664.mp4?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/b46473513d81d3fde9f55c621f5b1b1c.poster.avif?t=1773995248\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/b46473513d81d3fde9f55c621f5b1b1c.webm?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/b46473513d81d3fde9f55c621f5b1b1c.mp4?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Forge is a puzzle game where you create pixel art by connecting nodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rabbit turns into a bird, and a bird becomes a dolphin?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A seahorse and a dragon merge into a rapper?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With just nodes, anything is possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each of the over 50 nodes, including Add, Subtract, Shift, Rotate, Split, and Combine, has its own unique function.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect these nodes in various ways to transform pixel art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From Grayscale World, to RGB World, to Alpha World, to Emission World, and to Motion World where pixel art is animated, explore five worlds with different characteristics, and discover mind-blowing puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 stages across 5 worlds, each with its own unique personality.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic stages always introduce new nodes every time, allowing you to organically learn how they work.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advanced stages make use of the nodes learned in the basic stages in various ways.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There can be multiple ways to solve a puzzle. Use over 50 nodes to find your own solution.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contains a built-in hint system. Use hints if you get stuck!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Has an original soundtrack.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/dee08d9f892b3fc3113e196e4d9996e4.poster.avif?t=1773995248\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/dee08d9f892b3fc3113e196e4d9996e4.webm?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/dee08d9f892b3fc3113e196e4d9996e4.mp4?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/136f13af9b82e7d48909d2f9bb689664.poster.avif?t=1773995248\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/136f13af9b82e7d48909d2f9bb689664.webm?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/136f13af9b82e7d48909d2f9bb689664.mp4?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/b46473513d81d3fde9f55c621f5b1b1c.poster.avif?t=1773995248\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/b46473513d81d3fde9f55c621f5b1b1c.webm?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4410610/extras/b46473513d81d3fde9f55c621f5b1b1c.mp4?t=1773995248\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
